Package: mniw
Type: Package
Title: Density and Simulation for the Matrix-Normal Inverse-Wishart (MNIW) Distribution
Version: 0.0.0.9013
Date: 2016-06-03
Authors@R: c(person("Martin", "Lysy", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "mlysy@uwaterloo.ca"),
             person("Bryan", "Yates", role = "aut"))
Description: C++ implementations of Matrix-Normal Inverse-Wishart (MNIW) distributions and their constituent components using the Eigen linear algebra library.  All functions arguments accept scalar, vector, matrix, and array inputs whenever possible.  Also provides a Gibbs sampler for the posterior distribution of a matrix-valued random-effects model.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.6)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
